text.section:
The Department shall:
harmonize its planning activities with the planning activities of other units of the State government;
coordinate the plans and programs of all units of the State government;
cooperate with and assist other units of the State government in the execution of their planning functions, to harmonize their planning activities with the State Development Plan; and
promote the State's Economic Growth, Resource Protection, and Planning Policy set forth in Subtitle 7A of this title.
